Customer --> C12
Customer --> C13
Customer --> C14
Customer --> C15

' Provider → UC
Provider --> P1
Provider --> P2
Provider --> P4
Provider --> P5
Provider --> P6
Provider --> P10
Provider --> P11
Provider --> P12
Provider --> P13
Provider --> P14
Provider --> P17
Provider --> P18

' Admin → UC
Admin --> A1
Admin --> A2
Admin --> A3
Admin --> A4
Admin --> A5
Admin --> A6
Admin --> A7
Admin --> A8
Admin --> A9
Admin --> A10
Admin --> A11
Admin --> A12

' ==================== NOTES ====================

note right of C6
  **Create Order:**
  • Select date & time
  • Pick location on map
  • Add description & photos
  • Specify quantity
end note

note right of P1
  **Registration Steps:**
  1. Select categories
  2. Personal info
  3. Upload documents
    (KTP, selfie, portfolio,
     ijazah, certificates)
  4. KTP OCR scan
  5. Liveness detection
  6. Accept terms
  → Pending verification
end note

note right of A3
  **Provider Verification:**
  • Review uploaded KTP,
    selfie, ijazah, portfolio
  • Verify identity via OCR
    & liveness check
  • Approve or reject
    with notes
end note

note right of A6
  **Escrow Payment Flow:**
  1. Customer pays to
     admin rekber account
  2. Admin confirms payment
  3. Provider works
  4. Admin releases payout
     to provider
end note

@enduml
